descriptionHtml:
I received a request for the savegame to my Nord, who made her screen shot debut in my Tavern Clothes Retextured mod. So I submit, for your approval, Eirwen Stormbow at level 1, just arrived in Riverwood, at the Riverwood Traders. She still needs to speak to Gerdur. She is wearing the Tavern Clothes, though unless you download my retextured mod it won\'t be blue like the screen shots.

The screen shots are taken from my most recent save in Whiterun, so she doesn\'t have a circlet yet. A Blue one would look better.

For those who would like to ~showracemenu in the console on an existing game, I\'ve provided screenshots of Character Creation with the download. I have also provided directions in the readme.

I know there are a lot of savegames, but hopefully a few people will like her.

A Note on Mods:
These are the mods I\'m using in the screenshots:

1. This mod\'s #1 Texture (Glossy) femalehead.dds, 
2. #3 specular (soft) femalehead_s.dds, 
3. Amazing Smooth Females Complete normal maps (0-Smooth Females V3) femalehead_msn.dds, 
4. BellaGail\'s Eyeliner and Eyeshadow masks, 
5. And my own Pretty Lips. 

The body texture is Caliente\'s CBBE. 

Amazing Smooth Females Complete: http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=140 
BellaGail\'s Better Females: http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=2812 
Pretty Lips: http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=1167 
Caliente\'s Female Body Mod: http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=2666#
